{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1734790696.8889", "card_id": "Q_7298082565", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 98}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2024 年 11 月，人民币重回全球第四大最活跃货币，占比升至 3.89%，这反映了哪些信息？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "环球银行金融电信协会（Swift）当地时间 12 月 18 日发布的人民币月度报告和数据统计显示，今年 11 月，人民币在全球支付货币中的占比升至 3.89%，全球支付占比排名向前一位，升至第四大最活跃货币。具体而言，与 10 月相比，人民币支付金额总体增加了 22.12%，同时所有货币支付金额总体减少了 8.09%。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-7267db43b1534358309fe43548edfd4a_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "300 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/7298082565"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIrovj7v649rs1EAMaCTExMjQzNjMxOCC+3I+7BjAAOJECQAByCjcyOTgwODI1NjV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1734790696.11009", "card_id": "Q_7292229806", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 37}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待 25 考研政治肖四「翻车」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近十年最难的一次政治考试，考研过来人们如何看待这次的题目"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-19cf830c534431fc9194d40d87988b58_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "280 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/7292229806"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIrovj7v649rs1EAMaCTExMjQzNTE1NCCgvI+7BjAAOJkBQAFyCjcyOTIyMjk4MDZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1734790696.12420", "card_id": "Q_7440239116", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce